				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5974281#post-3823276</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5974281/team-bird-hub#post-3823276</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 03 Jun 2018 22:35:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Deadly Bread</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3988532</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>What I like about this team is the amount of SCPs that were created to make a story. The mind clock, the human satellite, the magic Christmas VHS, and the bird scientists. Most other teams are creating an SCP but then having other ones interact with that main one, but you guys are creating an entire reasoning. I wish I could give it more, but +1 will have to do.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5974281#post-3816577</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5974281/team-bird-hub#post-3816577</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 29 May 2018 06:56:42 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Here is a brief explanation of the general plot so far:</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers&nbsp;aweigh!</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">squawk</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>By some mechanism, the deity Thoth uses the Doomsday Clock (SCP-3662) as a conduit to transmit a stolen Avian meme complex (referenced in SPC-507) into all human minds. As a result, humans become less human-like and more bird-like (Join the Flock).</p> <p><strong>How does the Foundation know it was him?</strong> Because they detected him using a specialized satellite (SCP-3296) that detects reality-bending threats such as evil deities.</p> <p><strong>Why was he able to do what he did?</strong> Because the Foundation messed up big time and trapped Earth's resident Christian deity into a Christmas movie (SCP-3362).</p> <p><strong>And who is here to clean up the mess and save the day?</strong> MTF-Eta-4 &quot;Begone Thoth&quot; of the Avian Division (SCP-3095) and MFT CHARYBDIS of the Shark Punching Centre (SPC-507).</p> <p>Story to be continued in Act II!</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
